reviewText: I bought this because I met one of the cast members and she told me it was great.  Wrong! It is far from great. It is utter drivel. Totally the most ridiculous movie I have ever seen - avoid like you would a homeless person begging for change.
This truly is bad.  Not even in a campy, fun sort of way.  I resent the makers of this film for tricking me into watching it.
